com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.scp

Class ScpInboundContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.scp.ScpInboundContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITemplateRegistry

    public class ScpInboundContext
extends Object
implements ITemplateRegistry
    Responsible for providing SCP message templates to the session's FastInputStream. Based on these templates the session is able to decode SCP messages. When incoming SCP messages are decoded they are represented internally as IFIXMessage without msgType. Incoming SCP messages are consumed in the message assembly thread.
    Author:
    mmattini
